OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FThe US Supreme Court has rejected
OL,7,FDonald Trump's effort to limit
OL,8,Fbirthright citizenship, invalidating
OL,9,Fan executive order that was a key part
OL,10,Fof the president's agenda.
OL,12,FThe order would deny passports and
OL,13,Fother documents to children born to
OL,14,Fparents who are not citizens or green
OL,15,Fcard holders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
