OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782902882
OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FThe birthright citizenship order,
OL,7,Fwhich Trump signed on the first day of
OL,8,Fhis second term, was part of his
OL,9,Fadministration's broad immigration
OL,10,Fcrackdown . On Tuesday, the court
OL,11,Fstruck down that order by a 6-3 vote.
OL,13,FAn opinion written by Chief Justice
OL,14,FJohn Roberts held that the long-
OL,15,Fsettled understanding of the 14th
OL,16,FAmendment, adopted after the Civil
OL,17,FWar, makes a citizen of anyone born in
OL,18,Fthe United States, with very limited
OL,19,Fexceptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
