OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782902882
OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,F"Citizenship, then and now, was the
OL,7,Fright to have rights-to freely
OL,8,Fparticipate in our political
OL,9,Fcommunity" Chief Justice John Roberts
OL,10,Fwrote.
OL,12,F"The Framers of the Fourteenth
OL,13,FAmendment extended that promise to
OL,14,Fevery free-born person in this land.
OL,16,F"We keep that promise today."
OL,18,FThe US president's restrictions had
OL,19,Fbeen blocked by several lower courts
OL,20,Fand had not taken effect anywhere in
OL,21,Fthe US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
