OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FTrump said the decision was "too bad
OL,7,Ffor our Country" and wrongly suggested
OL,8,Fthat Congress could "easily" address
OL,9,Fit with legislation. The majority
OL,10,Fdecision rests on constitutional
OL,11,Fgrounds. It would take an amendment to
OL,12,Fovercome the decision.
OL,14,FDuring arguments in April, both
OL,15,Fconservative and liberal justices
OL,16,Fquestioned the order's legality in a
OL,17,Fmomentous case that was magnified by
OL,18,FTrump's unprecedented attendance in
OL,19,Fthe courtroom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
