OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FThe case framed another test of
OL,7,FTrump's assertions of executive power
OL,8,Fthat defy long-standing precedent for
OL,9,Fa court with a conservative majority
OL,10,Fand a robust view of presidential
OL,11,Fpower that has largely ruled in his
OL,12,Ffavor. In the notable exceptions when
OL,13,Fthe court has not, Trump has responded
OL,14,Fwith starkly personal criticisms of
OL,15,Fthe justices.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
