OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FBirthright citizenship was the first
OL,7,FTrump immigration-related policy to
OL,8,Freach the court for a final ruling.
OL,9,FThe justices previously struck down
OL,10,Fglobal tariffs Trump had imposed under
OL,11,Fan emergency powers law that had never
OL,12,Fbeen used that way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
