OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FHe seemed to recognise the court was
OL,7,Flikely to rule against him on
OL,8,Fbirthright citizenship, too, using his
OL,9,FTruth Social platform to criticize
OL,10,F"dumb judges and justices" and wealthy
OL,11,Fpregnant women from China and
OL,12,Felsewhere who come to the US to give
OL,13,Fbirth so their newborns will have
OL,14,FAmerican citizenship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
