OL,3,CUS Supreme Court rejects Trump's bid
OL,4,Cto limit birthright citizenship
OL,6,FMore than one-quarter of a million
OL,7,Fbabies born in the US each year would
OL,8,Fhave been affected by the executive
OL,9,Forder, according to research by the
OL,10,FMigration Policy Institute and
OL,11,FPennsylvania State University's
OL,12,FPopulation Research Institute.
OL,14,FWhile Trump has largely focused on
OL,15,Fillegal immigration in his rhetoric
OL,16,Fand actions, the birthright
OL,17,Fcitizenship restrictions also would
OL,18,Fhave applied to people who are legally
OL,19,Fin the United States, including
OL,20,Fstudents and applicants for green
OL,21,Fcards, or permanent resident status.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
